node.detail_zh: 患者無外遊紀錄，7 月 21 日出現症狀，由檢疫中心送院，與第 #1519 、 #1551 、 #1552 及 #1628 宗個案患者有關連。
node.detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history, started having symptoms on July 21, and was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre. Her case is epidemiologically related to the cases of patients #1519, #1551, #1552, and #1628.
node.classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
